cant wait for speedrunners2 this game is immaculate with friends cant really find online lobbies but if you want a fun competetive game among friends higly recommend

i love hurting people in last place its fun free and easy

dog shit controller support but fun game
very fun with a friend or with multiple friends me and my duo love to play this for something casual and fun
